  %font{:size => 4}
    Welcome to the Help page for the scenario SSH Inception. The purpose of this scenario
    is to familiarize you with the basics of ssh. We have also included some advanced
    challenges for students at more advanced levels.
    <br/>
    <br/>

  %font{:size => 4}
    %li
      %a
        = link_to 'Putty Download', 'http://www.putty.org/'
      <br/> Putty is an SSH and telnet client, because unlike every mature opperating system
      on the planet, Windows still doesn't ship with one.
      <br/>
      <br/>
    %li
      %a
        = link_to 'Dartmouth Putty Tutorial', 'http://www.cs.dartmouth.edu/~campbell/cs50/putty-cygwin-tutorial.pdf'
      <br/> A tutorial for Windows users new to Putty.
      <br/>
      <br/>
