        = link_to 'SSH Tutorial', 'http://support.suso.com/supki/SSH_Tutorial_for_Linux'
      <br/> This is an introduction and tutorial to ssh on linux, but it mostly applies to ssh on
      OSX as well. In the ssh_inception scenario, you will practice using ssh to connect from
      one server to the next, and then the next...
      <br/>
      <br/>

    %li
      %a
        = link_to 'Linux Command Tutorial', 'http://linuxcommand.org/lc3_lts0020.php'
